description: Gets a list of the work teams that you are subscribed to in the Amazon Web Services Marketplace. The list may be empty if no work team satisfies the filter specified in the NameContains parameter.

nested_items.name: SubscribedWorkteams
nested_items.description: An array of Workteam objects, each describing a work team.

nested_items.name: WorkteamArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the vendor that you have subscribed.

nested_items.name: MarketplaceTitle
nested_items.description: The title of the service provided by the vendor in the Amazon Marketplace.

nested_items.name: SellerName
nested_items.description: The name of the vendor in the Amazon Marketplace.

nested_items.name: MarketplaceDescription
nested_items.description: The description of the vendor from the Amazon Marketplace.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If the response is truncated, Amazon SageMaker returns this token. To retrieve the next set of work teams, use it in the subsequent request.
